{"id": 8031, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "1", "year": "2021", "session": "21M", "subtopic": "16-1-rate-expression-and-reaction-mechanism", "title": "21M.1.HL.TZ1.20", "topic_id": "16", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A reaction proceeds by the following mechanism:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">step 1: <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math><br/>step 2: <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">D</mi></math></p>\n<p>Which rate equation is consistent with this mechanism?</p>\n<p>A.  Rate = <em>k</em>[B]<sup>2</sup>[C]</p>\n<p>B.  Rate = <em>k</em>[A]<sup>2</sup>[B][C]</p>\n<p>C.  Rate = <em>k</em>[A]<sup>2</sup></p>\n<p>D.  Rate = <em>k</em>[A][C]</p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>C</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n[N/A]\n</div>"}